---
import ContactLayout from '../../layouts/ContactLayout.astro';
---
<ContactLayout title="Prices, rates and average cost for hiring a DJ" description="DJ Misha pricing and packages for weddings, corporate events, and private parties in San Diego. Get a custom quote for your event.">

  <h2>DJ Misha Pricing</h2>
  <p>DJ Misha offers competitive and transparent pricing for all events. Every event is unique, so pricing is customized based on your specific needs, event duration, location, and any additional services required.</p>

  <h3>Wedding DJ Packages</h3>
  <p>Wedding packages include pre-event consultation, ceremony music, cocktail hour, and full reception DJ services with professional sound and lighting.</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Pre-event consultation and personalized planning</li>
    <li>Ceremony, cocktail hour, and reception music</li>
    <li>Professional sound system for up to 500 guests</li>
    <li>Wireless microphones for toasts and speeches</li>
    <li>Dance lighting</li>
    <li>MC services available</li>
    <li>Custom playlists and "must play/do not play" lists</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Corporate Event DJ</h3>
  <p>Professional DJ services for corporate events, holiday parties, product launches, award ceremonies, and team building events.</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Background music and ambient sound management</li>
    <li>Dance floor entertainment</li>
    <li>Wireless microphones for presentations</li>
    <li>Customized playlists for your brand and event theme</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Private Party DJ</h3>
  <p>Top-of-the-line DJ and sound equipment for birthdays, anniversaries, graduations, and any private celebration.</p>

  <h3>DJ + Saxophone Package</h3>
  <p>The ultimate entertainment experience with DJ Misha and saxophonist Jason Whitmore performing together for a unique blend of live music and DJ performance.</p>

  <h3>Factors That Affect Pricing</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Type of event (wedding, corporate, private party)</li>
    <li>Duration of the event</li>
    <li>Number of guests</li>
    <li>Location and travel distance</li>
    <li>Additional equipment or lighting needs</li>
    <li>Add-on services (MC, saxophone, extra speakers)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Get a Custom Quote</h3>
  <p>Every event is different, and DJ Misha provides personalized quotes to ensure you get exactly what you need at a fair price. Contact us with your event details for a fast response.</p>

  <p><strong>Text or Call for a fast response: <a href="tel:6197862664">(619) 786-2664</a></strong></p>

  <ul class="actions">
    <li><a href="/contact/" class="button primary">Get a Quote</a></li>
  </ul>

</ContactLayout>
